WEBVTT

01:46.208 --> 01:48.417
PREVIOUSLY ON "DEXTER"...

01:50.125 --> 01:52.291
Angel: OPEN UP, PERRY,
IT'S THE POLICE. OPEN UP.

01:52.291 --> 01:54.250
HEY, ANGEL, I GOT HIM!

01:54.250 --> 01:56.208
Dexter: THEY REALLY FOUND
THE ICE-TRUCK KILLER?

01:56.208 --> 01:58.709
I SAW HIM, DEX.
I CHASED HIM.

01:58.709 --> 02:02.291
THE FUN PART WAS
HANGING THEM LIKE CATTLE

02:02.291 --> 02:04.375
RIGHT BEFORE
I CUT THEIR THROATS.

02:04.375 --> 02:06.000
SON OF A BITCH.

02:06.000 --> 02:08.500
Dexter: I HAVE
SO MANY QUESTIONS FOR HIM.

02:08.500 --> 02:11.166
WHAT WAS HIS MESSAGE TO ME?

02:11.166 --> 02:12.917
NOW I NEED TO KNOW HIM.

02:12.917 --> 02:14.709
HI.

02:14.709 --> 02:16.250
FUCK ARE YOU?

02:18.500 --> 02:20.583
PAUL BENNETT,
FATHER ON PAROLE.

02:20.583 --> 02:23.500
DEXTER MORGAN.

02:23.500 --> 02:25.125
I CAN'T THINK
OF ANYTHING CLEVER TO SAY.

02:25.125 --> 02:27.750
DIVORCE PAPERS --
SIGN THEM NOW,

02:27.750 --> 02:30.083
AND I'LL AGREE TO SUPERVISED
VISITS TWICE A WEEK.

02:30.083 --> 02:31.875
YOU THINK YOU CAN
REALLY MAKE ME BACK DOWN?

02:31.875 --> 02:33.834
ARE YOU FUCKING MY WIFE?

02:35.750 --> 02:38.250
I JUST WISH HE'D GO AWAY.

02:38.250 --> 02:40.625
I MEAN, WHY CAN'T HE JUST GO
AWAY AND DISAPPEAR FOREVER?

02:40.625 --> 02:43.083
ALL ALONG, I THOUGHT
THIS WAS A GAME

02:43.083 --> 02:46.208
MY ALTER EGO AND I
WERE PLAYING.

02:46.208 --> 02:50.917
BUT RELATIONSHIPS
CHANGE, EVOLVE,

02:50.917 --> 02:53.291
AND THIS ONE'S GETTING DEEP.

02:53.291 --> 02:56.792
I REALIZE NOW
MY DAYS ARE NUMBERED.

02:56.792 --> 02:59.500
SO I'D BETTER MAKE
THE MOST OF THEM.

03:02.000 --> 03:03.834
YOUR INSTINCTS
WERE DEAD-ON.

03:03.834 --> 03:06.375
THEY'RE ALWAYS DEAD-ON WHEN IT
COMES TO KILLERS. WHY IS THAT?

03:07.458 --> 03:09.000
I'M WATCHIN' YOU.

03:18.500 --> 03:20.875
[ THUNDER CRASHES ]

03:23.000 --> 03:24.917
WHAT ARE WE
LOOKING AT HERE?

03:24.917 --> 03:27.583
Angel: I'M THINKING
TWO CIRCUS CLOWNS DANCING.

03:27.583 --> 03:29.000
YOU?

03:29.000 --> 03:31.417
NO, IT LOOKS LIKE A LOBSTER.
SEE THE CLAWS?

03:33.458 --> 03:37.625
WHY DO BLOODSTAINS ALWAYS
LOOK LIKE CRUSTACEANS TO YOU?

03:37.625 --> 03:39.250
I LIKE SEAFOOD.

03:39.250 --> 03:43.041
RORSCHACH WOULD SAY YOU HAVE
A HARD TIME RELATING TO OTHERS.

03:43.041 --> 03:45.000
NOT AS HARD AS HER.

03:45.000 --> 03:47.000
IT DOES LOOK
LIKE A SUICIDE.

03:47.000 --> 03:48.792
CAN I GET SOME LIGHT
IN HERE, PLEASE?

03:48.792 --> 03:50.000
DAMN POWER OUTAGES.

03:50.000 --> 03:51.542
I DON'T KNOW, ANGEL.

03:51.542 --> 03:53.333
MOST FIREARM SUICIDES
ARE COMMITTED BY MEN.

03:53.333 --> 03:55.208
WOMEN SLASH THEIR WRISTS,
TAKE PILLS,

03:55.208 --> 03:56.417
SOMETHING MORE LADYLIKE.

03:56.417 --> 03:57.750
NOT IN MIAMI.

03:57.750 --> 03:59.792
WE CLOSED A COUPLE
OF SUICIDE CASES

03:59.792 --> 04:01.542
JUST LIKE THIS LAST YEAR,
REMEMBER?

04:05.542 --> 04:07.750
[ THUNDER CRASHES ]

04:07.750 --> 04:09.291
LOOK AT THIS MESS.

04:09.291 --> 04:11.166
THAT'S A FANCY BATHTUB.
RICH HUSBAND?

04:11.166 --> 04:13.709
HOUSE HUSBAND
AND ASPIRING ARTIST.

04:13.709 --> 04:16.709
OOH. PROMISING.
SO, SHE  SUPPORTED  HIM?

04:16.709 --> 04:18.166
IT LOOKS LIKE THAT.

04:18.166 --> 04:19.959
SHE WAS SOME KIND
OF BIG-TIME PROSECUTOR.

04:19.959 --> 04:21.709
THOSE OTHER SUICIDES
WE CLOSED --

04:21.709 --> 04:24.041
THOSE WERE HIGH-POWERED WOMEN,
TOO, RIGHT?

04:24.041 --> 04:25.834
I DON'T KNOW.
I THINK SO.

04:25.834 --> 04:28.458
NOTE TO SELF.

04:30.417 --> 04:32.667
Gayle: I DON'T CARE WHAT IT
LOOKS LIKE. SOMEBODY KILLED HER.

04:32.667 --> 04:34.959
Doakes: WE'RE CHECKING OUT
ALL THE POSSIBILITIES.

04:34.959 --> 04:38.375
WAS YOUR WIFE DEALING
WITH ANY EMOTIONAL PROBLEM?

04:38.375 --> 04:40.291
YOU KNOW,
JOB STRESS, THE USUAL,

04:40.291 --> 04:42.041
BUT SHE WAS WORKING
THROUGH IT IN THERAPY.

04:42.041 --> 04:44.458
SHE HAVE ANY OTHER PROBLEMS
THAT YOU'RE AWARE OF?

04:44.458 --> 04:47.709
ARE YOU LISTENING TO ME?
VANESSA DIDN'T KILL HERSELF.

04:47.709 --> 04:50.208
CRIMINALS STAGE SUICIDES
ALL THE TIME.

04:50.208 --> 04:52.208
WE'LL CHECK INTO IT.

04:52.208 --> 04:54.417
WE NEED TO COLLECT YOUR CLOTHES
FOR EVIDENCE --

04:54.417 --> 04:56.250
STANDARD PROCEDURE.

04:56.250 --> 04:58.667
[ THUNDER CRASHES ]

05:08.041 --> 05:10.458
COME ON. I GOT TO GO. THERE'S
A DEAD BODY IN THAT HOUSE.

05:10.458 --> 05:12.208
THERE'S A HOT BODY
IN HERE.

05:12.208 --> 05:14.542
I SO WANT
TO MAUL YOU RIGHT NOW.

05:14.542 --> 05:18.000
I SO WANT YOU TO.
CALL ME WHEN YOU'RE DONE, OKAY?

05:18.000 --> 05:20.000
I'LL BRING HANDCUFFS.

05:29.166 --> 05:31.917
MORGAN,
WHAT TOOK YOU SO LONG?

05:31.917 --> 05:34.750
PLAYING "HIDE THE SALAMI"
WITH MR. PROSTHETICS?

05:34.750 --> 05:37.125
I DON'T FUCK AND TELL.
SINCE WHEN?

05:37.125 --> 05:38.792
CAN WE GO INSIDE?
I'M KIND OF WET.

05:38.792 --> 05:40.291
DON'T.

05:40.291 --> 05:42.250
NO, I NEED YOU TO FIND OUT

05:42.250 --> 05:44.250
ABOUT THE VICTIM'S RELATIONSHIP
WITH HER HUSBAND.

05:44.250 --> 05:46.333
IT'S ALWAYS
THE HUSBAND, RIGHT?

05:46.333 --> 05:47.875
LOOKS LIKE A SUICIDE,
BUT YOU NEVER KNOW --

05:47.875 --> 05:49.583
YOUNGER GUY, UNEMPLOYED.

05:49.583 --> 05:52.041
MAYBE HE WAS A BOY TOY
AND KILLED HER FOR HER MONEY.

05:52.041 --> 05:53.166
I'M ON IT.

05:54.875 --> 05:57.458
DOAKES IS SENDING YOU AWAY
FROM A CRIME SCENE IN RAIN

05:57.458 --> 05:59.125
AND YOU'RE NOT
PUTTING UP A FIGHT?

05:59.125 --> 06:01.000
I'M A TEAM PLAYER.
YOU ARE?

06:01.000 --> 06:02.834
FUCK YOU!

06:02.834 --> 06:05.959
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

06:05.959 --> 06:08.333
OH, HEY, DEX,
COME ON IN.

06:12.917 --> 06:14.208
WHERE'S RITA?

06:14.208 --> 06:15.792
UH, SHE'S STUCK
IN TRAFFIC.

06:15.792 --> 06:18.000
POWER'S OUT
IN HALF THE CITY.

06:18.000 --> 06:19.875
OF COURSE, I LOVE
THE EXTRA KID TIME,

06:19.875 --> 06:24.166
BUT, UH, COURT SUPERVISOR --
NOT SO MUCH.

06:24.166 --> 06:26.333
[ CHILDREN LAUGHING ]

06:26.333 --> 06:28.291
HEY, YOU KNOW,
I FEEL REALLY BAD

06:28.291 --> 06:30.375
ABOUT THE LAST TIME
I WAS HERE.

06:30.375 --> 06:32.625
I DIDN'T MEAN TO GET
ALL ALPHA MALE ON YOU.

06:32.625 --> 06:34.917
WHAT ARE YOU SUPPOSED
TO SAY TO THE GUY

06:34.917 --> 06:36.834
WHO'S F'ING YOUR WIFE
WHILE YOU'RE IN JAIL?

06:36.834 --> 06:39.000
[ DOOR OPENS ]

06:39.000 --> 06:42.333
SORRY. SORRY I'M LATE.

06:42.333 --> 06:44.583
THANKS FOR HOLDING DOWN
THE FORT.

06:44.583 --> 06:46.333
DO YOU MIND IF I GET GOING?

06:46.333 --> 06:47.792
I GOT KIDS OF MY OWN
AT HOME TO LOOK AFTER.

06:47.792 --> 06:49.333
NO, NO, NO.
IT'S OKAY.

06:49.333 --> 06:50.792
DEXTER AND I
ARE HERE NOW.

06:50.792 --> 06:52.125
BYE, KIDS.

06:52.125 --> 06:54.000
MOM, DEXTER,
THE LIGHTS ARE OUT.

06:54.000 --> 06:56.000
THEY ARE?
HEY, I BROUGHT HOT CHOCOLATE.

06:56.000 --> 06:58.166
DAD ALREADY MADE US SOME.

06:58.166 --> 07:00.125
WITH EXTRA MARSHMALLOWS.

07:00.125 --> 07:02.291
TAG -- YOU'RE IT!

07:02.291 --> 07:03.709
I'D LOVE
SOME HOT CHOCOLATE.

07:03.709 --> 07:06.041
TAKE TWO.
LOOKS LIKE HE'S GOT EXTRA.

07:06.041 --> 07:07.834
COME HERE, BUDDY.

07:07.834 --> 07:12.667
MOM, CAN DAD STAY
AND PUT US TO BED, PLEASE?

07:12.667 --> 07:15.000
I THINK THAT'S WHY
DEXTER'S HERE, SWEETIE.

07:15.000 --> 07:15.875
DEXTER DOESN'T MIND.

07:15.875 --> 07:17.750
YAY!

07:17.750 --> 07:20.291
ONLY A SONG, NO STORY --
IT'S WAY PAST YOUR BEDTIME.

07:20.291 --> 07:23.583
ALL RIGHT, BEDBUGS,
LET'S LEAVE THESE TWO ALONE.

07:23.583 --> 07:26.208
IT'S NOT LIKE
THEY NEED A CHAPERONE.

07:37.375 --> 07:40.166
MEGHAN DOWD, CAROLYN JILLIAN,
AND NOW VANESSA GAYLE --

07:40.166 --> 07:42.083
ALL THREE POWERFUL WOMEN,

07:42.083 --> 07:44.834
ALL THREE SHOT THEMSELVES
IN THE PAST TWO YEARS.

07:44.834 --> 07:46.917
THEY'VE GOT TO HAVE
MORE IN COMMON

07:46.917 --> 07:49.667
THAN CAREER AMBITION
AND A FONDNESS OF FIREARMS.

07:49.667 --> 07:52.792
WHY THE SUDDEN INTEREST
IN SUICIDES?

07:52.792 --> 07:55.917
MORBID CURIOSITY.

07:55.917 --> 07:58.083
WHAT CAN I DO FOR YOU?

07:58.083 --> 08:00.041
SO MANY THINGS.

08:00.041 --> 08:02.792
I NEED THE BLOOD-SPATTER REPORT
ON VANESSA GAYLE.

08:02.792 --> 08:05.583
[ SIGHS ]

08:05.583 --> 08:07.375
BLOOD SPATTER'S INCONCLUSIVE.

08:07.375 --> 08:09.542
ALL I CAN TELL IS SHE WAS
SHOT AT CLOSE RANGE.

08:09.542 --> 08:10.834
I WISH
I HAD MORE FOR YOU.

08:10.834 --> 08:13.291
ME TOO.

08:13.291 --> 08:16.333
MARIA, THE D.A.
NEEDS THE WORK SHEET

08:16.333 --> 08:18.166
FOR THE ICE-TRUCK-KILLER CASE.

08:18.166 --> 08:20.500
I'M WORKING ON IT.
WHEN'D YOU TALK TO THE D.A.?

08:20.500 --> 08:22.458
WE HAD DINNER LAST NIGHT.

08:22.458 --> 08:25.208
MAYOR ALLEN TOOK US OUT TO
CELEBRATE NEIL PERRY'S ARREST --

08:25.208 --> 08:27.959
HELL OF A GOOD TIME.

08:27.959 --> 08:30.959
HMM. YOU PUTA.

08:30.959 --> 08:32.750
I'M THE ONE WHO GETS
PERRY TO CONFESS,

08:32.750 --> 08:34.500
AND HE'S GOT THE MAYOR
KISSING HIS ASS.

08:34.500 --> 08:36.125
I WOULDN'T BE TOO UPSET.

08:36.125 --> 08:38.417
MATTHEWS WILL BE THE ONE
WITH THE EGG ON HIS FACE.

08:38.417 --> 08:40.166
YOU STILL BELIEVE
WE GOT THE WRONG GUY?

08:40.166 --> 08:42.083
PERRY'S THE PRETENDER
TO THE THRONE.

08:42.083 --> 08:44.458
THE REAL KING IS STILL OUT
THERE, AND HE'LL KILL AGAIN.

08:44.458 --> 08:46.000
IT'S JUST A MATTER OF TIME.

08:46.000 --> 08:47.500
OR THE ICE-TRUCK KILLER
WILL USE PERRY

08:47.500 --> 08:49.208
AS A GET-OUT-OF-JAIL-FREE
CARD.

08:52.125 --> 08:54.625
YOU REALLY THINK
THAT MIGHT HAPPEN?

08:54.625 --> 08:56.709
IF PERRY'S THE WRONG GUY

08:56.709 --> 09:00.000
AND I LET HIM TAKE
THE FALL, DEFINITELY.

09:00.000 --> 09:02.208
THANKS, DEXTER.

09:02.208 --> 09:04.166
WHAT IF LaGUERTA'S RIGHT?

09:04.166 --> 09:07.667
WHAT IF THE ICE-TRUCK KILLER
DOES DISAPPEAR?

09:10.750 --> 09:13.917
NO. HE'S GOT
UNFINISHED BUSINESS WITH ME.

09:13.917 --> 09:16.041
STILL, I CAN'T JUST SIT
ON MY HANDS

09:16.041 --> 09:18.083
WAITING FOR SOMETHING
TO HAPPEN.

09:18.083 --> 09:21.500
I NEED A DISTRACTION.

09:21.500 --> 09:23.625
NOTHING LIKE
SOME LITTLE DEBBIES

09:23.625 --> 09:27.041
AND A WORTHY NEW ADVERSARY
TO CLEAR OUT THE OLD NOGGIN.

09:27.041 --> 09:29.000
[ DRAWER CLOSES ]

09:32.250 --> 09:34.542
TALK TO ME, LADIES.

09:34.542 --> 09:37.500
WHAT DO YOU HAVE IN COMMON?

09:37.500 --> 09:41.667
SAME SORORITY?
PILATES INSTRUCTOR?

09:58.583 --> 10:01.709
DR. EMMETT MERIDIAN.

10:06.417 --> 10:09.834
THE THREE SUICIDE SISTERS
SHARED THE SAME THERAPIST --

10:09.834 --> 10:12.250
DR. EMMETT MERIDIAN.

10:12.250 --> 10:15.208
HE MUST BE TERRIBLE AT HIS JOB.

10:24.709 --> 10:27.417
SO FAR, HE COMES UP
SQUEAKY CLEAN --

10:27.417 --> 10:30.792
NO MALPRACTICE SUITS,
NO DISGRUNTLED PATIENTS.

10:30.792 --> 10:34.083
AND I THOUGHT  I  WAS A MASTER
AT DAMAGE CONTROL.

10:34.083 --> 10:37.625
PERHAPS I SHOULD SCHEDULE
A SESSION WITH THE GOOD DOCTOR

10:37.625 --> 10:40.750
AND TRY OUT A LITTLE
REVERSE PSYCHOLOGY.

10:40.750 --> 10:43.166
COME ON IN, SEAN.
HAVE A SEAT.

10:43.166 --> 10:46.000
THANKS FOR SEEING ME
ON SUCH SHORT NOTICE.

10:46.000 --> 10:48.667
HEY, I EXPECT THE POLICE
TO SHOW UP WHEN I CALL, RIGHT?

10:48.667 --> 10:51.291
THE LEAST I CAN DO IS CLEAR
MY LUNCH HOUR FOR A COP IN NEED.

10:51.291 --> 10:55.333
SO, WHAT BROUGHT YOU HERE?

10:55.333 --> 10:57.834
A FRIEND OF MINE DIED.

11:01.375 --> 11:04.041
SHE KILLED HERSELF.

11:04.041 --> 11:06.083
I NEED TO UNDERSTAND WHY.

11:06.083 --> 11:07.750
HOW COME?

11:07.750 --> 11:09.625
SHE HAD EVERYTHING GOING
FOR HER. IT DOESN'T MAKE SENSE.

11:09.625 --> 11:12.792
TO SOME PEOPLE,
DEATH MAKES PERFECT SENSE.

11:12.792 --> 11:15.458
LIFE --
NOW, THAT'S THE PUZZLE,

11:15.458 --> 11:17.625
LIKE YOU, SEAN.

11:17.625 --> 11:20.083
WHAT REALLY
BROUGHT YOU HERE?

11:20.083 --> 11:21.709
I JUST TOLD YOU I CAME --

11:21.709 --> 11:23.625
TO TALK ABOUT
YOUR FRIEND'S SUICIDE, I KNOW.

11:23.625 --> 11:26.000
I THINK YOU'RE USING
THIS SUICIDE DEAL

11:26.000 --> 11:27.792
AS AN EXCUSE
TO COME SEE ME.

11:31.041 --> 11:32.792
YOU'RE ABSOLUTELY RIGHT.

11:36.250 --> 11:38.375
HOW COULD YOU TELL?

11:38.375 --> 11:39.792
I'M SENSING YOU DO IT A LOT

11:39.792 --> 11:41.542
TO KEEP THE WORLD
AT ARM'S LENGTH.

11:41.542 --> 11:45.291
AND WHAT ARE
MY REAL INTENTIONS?

11:47.291 --> 11:48.917
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

11:48.917 --> 11:52.375
AS SOON
AS I PAY FOR MY LUNCH,

11:52.375 --> 11:54.458
YOU'RE GONNA TELL ME THAT.

11:54.458 --> 11:56.208
EXCUSE ME A SECOND.

11:56.208 --> 11:59.291
JUDGING FROM WHAT I'VE SEEN
SO FAR, I PROBABLY WILL.

11:59.291 --> 12:00.917
THIS GUY'S GOOD.

12:00.917 --> 12:03.500
SO WHY DO
HIS PATIENTS KEEP DYING?

12:05.709 --> 12:07.834
VANESSA'S ESTIMATED TIME
OF DEATH

12:07.834 --> 12:10.583
WAS MONDAY AT 7:00 P.M.

12:10.583 --> 12:13.333
MERIDIAN WAS IN SESSION
WITH SCOTT SOLOMON.

12:13.333 --> 12:17.709
I WONDER IF MR. SOLOMON KEPT
HIS APPOINTMENT THAT NIGHT.

12:20.792 --> 12:25.667
SO, WE GOT ALMOND CHICKEN,
PORK FRIED RICE.

12:25.667 --> 12:28.166
SO, SEAN, LET'S START
WITH THE BASICS. YOU MARRIED?

12:28.166 --> 12:29.917
NO.

12:29.917 --> 12:31.166
GIRLFRIEND?

12:31.166 --> 12:33.083
YES.

12:33.083 --> 12:35.000
SEX LIFE?

12:35.000 --> 12:37.083
IT'S PERSONAL.

12:37.083 --> 12:39.959
AND THIS IS THERAPY,
WHERE WE SHARE PERSONAL THINGS.

12:44.291 --> 12:46.000
YOU KNOW, IT MIGHT
HELP ME OPEN UP

12:46.000 --> 12:47.959
IF YOU SHARED SOMETHING
ABOUT YOURSELF.

12:47.959 --> 12:49.625
WHY DID YOU BECOME
A PSYCHIATRIST?

12:49.625 --> 12:52.709
SEE WHAT YOU JUST DID?

12:52.709 --> 12:56.208
TRYING TO TAKE CONTROL
LIKE THAT?

12:56.208 --> 12:59.208
YOU PROBABLY GET AWAY WITH IT
MOST OF THE TIME, TOO, RIGHT?

12:59.208 --> 13:01.583
THAT'S A WAY
OF PREVENTING OTHER PEOPLE

13:01.583 --> 13:03.208
FROM GETTING CLOSE TO YOU.

13:03.208 --> 13:05.208
LET ME
ASK YOU SOMETHING, SEAN.

13:09.834 --> 13:12.375
HAVE YOU EVER BEEN
CLOSE TO ANYBODY?

13:16.583 --> 13:18.917
MY FOSTER FATHER.

13:20.875 --> 13:23.291
HE'S THE ONLY ONE
WHO EVER REALLY KNEW ME.

13:23.291 --> 13:26.041
YOU'RE ADOPTED?

13:26.041 --> 13:28.917
HARRY TOOK ME IN
WHEN I WAS 3.

13:28.917 --> 13:31.417
SO TELL ME ABOUT HARRY.

13:31.417 --> 13:34.834
WHAT KIND OF STUFF
DID YOU GUYS DO TOGETHER?

13:34.834 --> 13:37.250
YOU KNOW,
NORMAL FATHER-SON STUFF.

13:41.250 --> 13:42.458
[ CHOKING ]

13:42.458 --> 13:45.917
[ GLASS SHATTERS ]

13:45.917 --> 13:48.333
ALL RIGHT. STOP.
ENOUGH.

13:48.333 --> 13:50.583
[ COUGHING ]

13:50.583 --> 13:52.500
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

13:52.500 --> 13:55.625
I'M FINE. I'M FINE.

13:55.625 --> 13:57.792
NICE AMBUSH.

13:57.792 --> 14:00.041
THAT WAS THE PERFECT
POINT OF ATTACK.

14:00.041 --> 14:01.792
I CAN'T BELIEVE
I FINALLY GOT YOU.

14:01.792 --> 14:03.625
I WON.

14:03.625 --> 14:07.417
THIS ISN'T A GAME,
DEXTER.

14:07.417 --> 14:08.667
NO, I-I KNOW.

14:08.667 --> 14:11.000
IT'S NOT SUPPOSED
TO BE FUN.

14:11.000 --> 14:12.792
YEAH.
YEAH, YEAH, IT'S JUST --

14:12.792 --> 14:15.125
YOU THINK I WANT
TO TEACH YOU THESE THINGS?

14:15.125 --> 14:16.875
THIS IS THE ONLY WAY I KNOW

14:16.875 --> 14:19.500
HOW TO KEEP YOU
OUT OF AN ELECTRIC CHAIR.

14:19.500 --> 14:23.125
THIS IS ABOUT SURVIVAL, DEX,
NOTHING ELSE.

14:23.125 --> 14:25.041
GOT IT?

14:42.834 --> 14:44.625
Man: YOU'VE GOT
A VISITOR, PERRY.

14:44.625 --> 14:45.625
MISS ME?

14:45.625 --> 14:47.291
DON'T FLATTER YOURSELF.

14:47.291 --> 14:50.000
I HAVE TO COMB THROUGH YOUR CASE
BEFORE THE TRIAL,

14:50.000 --> 14:52.208
MAKE SURE
I HAVE MY FACTS STRAIGHT

14:52.208 --> 14:54.250
ON THE NOTORIOUS
ICE-TRUCK KILLER.

14:54.250 --> 14:58.125
UM, I CONFESSED.
WHAT MORE DO YOU NEED?

14:58.125 --> 14:59.583
THE EVIDENCE TO LINE UP.

14:59.583 --> 15:01.291
WE HAVEN'T BEEN ABLE
TO MATCH YOUR PRINTS

15:01.291 --> 15:03.166
AGAINST THE PARTIAL
ON THE LOZENGE WRAPPER

15:03.166 --> 15:05.166
WE FOUND
AT THE ABANDONED HOSPITAL.

15:05.166 --> 15:08.208
LIQUID NITROGEN -- I USE IT
TO FREEZE THE BODY PARTS.

15:08.208 --> 15:11.250
IT'S EXTREMELY EFFECTIVE,
BUT IT BURNS LIKE A BITCH.

15:11.250 --> 15:12.875
OH.

15:12.875 --> 15:16.166
OR YOU KNEW YOUR PRINTS
WOULDN'T MATCH,

15:16.166 --> 15:19.083
SO YOU PURPOSELY BURNED
YOUR FINGERTIPS TO HIDE IT.

15:19.083 --> 15:22.208
ARE YOU SUGGESTING
THAT I'M A LIAR?

15:22.208 --> 15:25.500
JUST COVERING MY BASES, NEIL.
WE BOTH WANT THE SAME THING.

15:25.500 --> 15:29.125
UH...10 MINUTES ALONE
WITH ANGELINA?

15:29.125 --> 15:31.041
TO SEE YOU CONVICTED.

15:34.125 --> 15:37.750
WHAT'S IN IT FOR ME
IF I HELP YOU DO YOUR JOB?

15:37.750 --> 15:40.542
HMM...

15:40.542 --> 15:42.875
HOW ABOUT IMMORTALITY?

15:47.250 --> 15:49.875
WE FOUND YOUR MOTHER'S BODY
UNDER YOUR HOUSE.

15:49.875 --> 15:52.709
NOW, YOU CAN GO DOWN AS
A PATHETIC LOSER WHO KILLED MOM

15:52.709 --> 15:57.417
OR THE MOST HEINOUS KILLER

15:57.417 --> 16:00.500
IN FLORIDA'S HISTORY --

16:00.500 --> 16:02.083
YOUR CHOICE.

16:06.583 --> 16:09.709
IF I'M GOING
TO BECOME A LEGEND,

16:09.709 --> 16:11.208
I NEED TO BE MEMORIALIZED.

16:11.208 --> 16:14.458
I WANT A REPORTER HERE
TO INTERVIEW ME -- FRONT PAGE.

16:14.458 --> 16:17.166
YOU'RE NOT ALLOWED TO TALK
TO THE PRESS BEFORE THE TRIAL.

16:17.166 --> 16:20.583
IF YOU WANT ME
TO COOPERATE,

16:20.583 --> 16:24.083
I'M SURE YOU'LL FIND A WAY.

16:31.333 --> 16:35.291
MERIDIAN HAD ONE THING RIGHT.
I DO CRAVE CONTROL.

16:35.291 --> 16:39.375
THE LONGER THE ICE-TRUCK KILLER
MAINTAINS RADIO SILENCE,

16:39.375 --> 16:41.250
THE LESS CONTROL I HAVE.

16:41.250 --> 16:46.125
Craigslist -- IT'S DESPERATE,
I KNOW, BUT APROPOS.

16:46.125 --> 16:49.041
PERSONAL ADS ARE FILLED
WITH DESPERATION.

16:49.041 --> 16:53.125
"TYLER FROM KEY WEST,"
"SPEEDOS TANNING ON THE BEACH,"

16:53.125 --> 16:55.250
"TOUCHED YOUR TITS
ON FRIDAY NIGHT" --

16:55.250 --> 16:58.041
AT LEAST THESE FOLKS
AREN'T JUST STANDING BY

16:58.041 --> 17:01.125
WAITING FOR SOMETHING
TO HAPPEN, AND NEITHER AM I.

17:03.834 --> 17:07.542
"DEAR KEN, I'M IN PIECES.

17:07.542 --> 17:11.333
WHY THE COLD SHOULDER?
LOVE, BARBIE."

17:14.333 --> 17:15.709
[ BEEP ]

17:27.667 --> 17:30.417
HEY, I GOT IT.

17:30.417 --> 17:32.291
THANKS.

17:32.291 --> 17:35.166
HEY, I KNOW YOU --
MONDAY NIGHT AT MERIDIAN'S.

17:35.166 --> 17:37.834
YOU'RE ALWAYS LEAVING YOUR 7:00
WHEN I'M ARRIVING FOR MY 8:00.

17:37.834 --> 17:39.333
YOU MISSED LAST WEEK, RIGHT?

17:39.333 --> 17:40.917
NO, I WAS THERE.

17:40.917 --> 17:42.834
I DON'T REMEMBER
EVER SEEING YOU, THOUGH.

17:42.834 --> 17:44.583
HOW DO YOU LIKE HIM?

17:44.583 --> 17:45.959
MERIDIAN?

17:45.959 --> 17:48.041
BEST THING THAT'S
EVER HAPPENED TO ME...

17:48.041 --> 17:49.875
SO FAR.

17:49.875 --> 17:52.041
HOW ABOUT YOU?
YOU FINDING HIM HELPFUL?

17:52.041 --> 17:53.375
I'M A SOCIOPATH.

17:53.375 --> 17:55.542
THERE'S NOT MUCH
HE CAN DO FOR ME.

17:55.542 --> 17:58.166
CUTE AND FUNNY.

17:58.166 --> 18:00.333
LET ME GUESS -- TAKEN.

18:00.333 --> 18:03.250
GIRLFRIEND.
LUCKY GIRL.

18:03.250 --> 18:06.125
WELL, THANKS FOR THE HELP,
BUT I CAN HANDLE IT FROM HERE.

18:06.125 --> 18:07.542
ALL RIGHT.

18:07.542 --> 18:10.625
SO MERIDIAN HAS AN ALIBI
FOR THE TIME OF DEATH.

18:10.625 --> 18:14.375
MY SEXUAL HANG-UPS
AND CONTROL ISSUES ASIDE,

18:14.375 --> 18:18.875
I NEED A FOLLOW-UP APPOINTMENT
TO DIG A LITTLE DEEPER.

18:18.875 --> 18:21.709
ISN'T THAT
WHAT THERAPY'S ALL ABOUT?

18:21.709 --> 18:23.542
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

18:55.959 --> 18:57.792
OH, MY GOD.

18:57.792 --> 19:00.250
I LOVE YOUR BODY.

19:04.083 --> 19:06.458
I LOVE YOUR LEGS.

19:08.417 --> 19:10.333
I LOVE YOUR ARMS.

19:12.250 --> 19:14.458
I COULDN'T HAVE MADE THEM
BETTER MYSELF.

19:16.792 --> 19:19.750
HEY.

19:19.750 --> 19:21.333
ARE YOU CRYING?

19:22.792 --> 19:24.083
I'M FINE.

19:26.583 --> 19:28.458
THEN WHAT?

19:30.500 --> 19:32.291
I DON'T KNOW.

19:35.291 --> 19:38.834
I'M SURE THIS IS REALLY HOT,
CRYING AFTER SEX.

19:38.834 --> 19:42.125
EVERYTHING ABOUT YOU IS HOT.

19:44.709 --> 19:46.875
TELL ME
WHAT YOU'RE FEELING.

19:52.667 --> 19:54.500
IT'S...

19:56.709 --> 19:58.792
IT'S JUST...

19:58.792 --> 20:01.542
EVERY TIME I'VE EVER
BEEN NAKED WITH SOMEONE...

20:04.291 --> 20:06.500
...WE JUST FUCK.

20:08.208 --> 20:11.500
BUT NOT THIS TIME?

20:11.500 --> 20:14.709
THIS IS DIFFERENT.

20:14.709 --> 20:16.208
IT FEELS LIKE...

20:18.458 --> 20:22.041
I HATE SAYING THIS.
IT SOUNDS SO FUCKING CHEESY.

20:22.041 --> 20:25.291
IT FEELS
LIKE MAKING LOVE.

20:25.291 --> 20:27.417
EW.

20:29.500 --> 20:32.959
YES.

20:32.959 --> 20:36.917
BUT, EW, PROMISE ME
YOU'LL NEVER SAY THAT AGAIN.

20:36.917 --> 20:39.000
WHAT IF I DO?

20:39.000 --> 20:41.333
ARE YOU GONNA CRY ABOUT IT?

20:43.750 --> 20:45.834
YOU'RE SO FUCKED UP.

20:45.834 --> 20:48.417
WHAT'S UP, ROCK STAR?

20:50.291 --> 20:52.959
LOOK AT YOU.

20:52.959 --> 20:54.875
WHAT YOU DOING? HEY.

20:56.875 --> 20:58.375
WHERE'S THE SUPERVISOR?

20:58.375 --> 21:00.458
OH, SHE CALLED ON MY CELL
AND CANCELED.

21:00.458 --> 21:02.709
WHO WANTS TO PLAY
MONSTER TAG?

21:02.709 --> 21:04.000
I DO.
YEAH?

21:04.000 --> 21:06.166
I'M COMING AFTER YOU.

21:06.166 --> 21:08.500
YOU BETTER RUN.

21:08.500 --> 21:11.166
PAUL, YOU KNOW YOU'RE NOT
ALLOWED UNSUPERVISED VISITS.

21:11.166 --> 21:14.041
I KNOW. BIG BAD PAUL
NEEDS A BABYSITTER.

21:14.041 --> 21:16.458
IT'S YOUR DAY OFF, RIGHT?

21:16.458 --> 21:19.166
NOW, WOULD IT REALLY BE
SO TERRIBLE

21:19.166 --> 21:21.125
IF WE SPENT TIME
WITH OUR KIDS TOGETHER?

21:21.125 --> 21:23.250
I HAVE A LUNCH DATE
WITH DEXTER.

21:23.250 --> 21:24.709
COME ON. IT'LL BE FUN.

21:26.041 --> 21:27.959
MOM, DAD, COME ON.

21:33.208 --> 21:36.834
I GUESS
I COULD CALL DEXTER.

21:36.834 --> 21:39.834
IT'S OFFICIAL -- I'M NOMINATING
YOU FOR MOM OF THE YEAR.

21:39.834 --> 21:41.458
[ SMOOCHES ]

21:41.458 --> 21:44.625
HERE COMES THE MONSTER.
HERE COMES THE MONSTER.

21:50.792 --> 21:53.291
CONTRARY TO WHAT
DR. MERIDIAN THINKS,

21:53.291 --> 21:55.834
I DON'T ALWAYS KEEP OTHERS
AT A DISTANCE.

21:55.834 --> 21:58.417
THINGS ARE LOOKING UP ALREADY.

22:02.166 --> 22:04.417
OR NOT.

22:04.417 --> 22:08.417
CLEARLY NOBODY HERE IS
MY MISSING PARTNER IN CRIME.

22:09.542 --> 22:11.542
HEY, WHAT'S UP?
YOU WERE LOOKING FOR ME?

22:11.542 --> 22:14.125
WHAT DID FORENSICS COME BACK
WITH ON VANESSA GAYLE?

22:14.125 --> 22:16.792
GUNPOWDER ON HER HAND,
NONE ON HER HUSBAND'S,

22:16.792 --> 22:19.792
HIGH-ANGLE TRAJECTORY,
NO DRUGS IN THE TOX SCREEN.

22:19.792 --> 22:21.709
IT ALL POINTS TO SUICIDE.

22:21.709 --> 22:23.500
NO CHANCE IT WAS MURDER?

22:23.500 --> 22:25.667
TOO BAD, HUH?
I HAD THE HUSBAND PEGGED, TOO.

22:25.667 --> 22:28.333
WAS HOPING HE COULD HELP ME
SCORE MY OWN SUGAR MAMA.

22:28.333 --> 22:29.333
TRY craigslist.

22:29.333 --> 22:30.709
I ALREADY DID --

22:30.709 --> 22:33.542
NOTHING BUT CAT LADIES
AND SAGGY TITS.

22:35.750 --> 22:37.667
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

22:37.667 --> 22:40.583
MIAMI METRO CAN CLOSE
THIS CASE AS A SUICIDE,

22:40.583 --> 22:43.000
BUT I'M STILL NOT CONVINCED.

22:43.000 --> 22:46.709
MAYBE MY NEW THERAPIST CAN SHED
SOME LIGHT ON MY DOUBTS.

22:46.709 --> 22:49.500
YOU SEEM ON EDGE TODAY.

22:49.500 --> 22:52.333
[ SIGHS ]

22:52.333 --> 22:54.250
I'M NOT GETTING
WHAT I CAME HERE FOR.

22:54.250 --> 22:55.834
WHAT'D YOU COME HERE FOR?

22:55.834 --> 22:58.041
WE ESTABLISHED
IN OUR LAST VISIT

22:58.041 --> 23:00.333
THAT IT WASN'T TO TALK
ABOUT SUICIDE.

23:00.333 --> 23:03.500
OR FEELINGS.
HEAVEN FORBID.

23:03.500 --> 23:05.750
SO, WHAT DO YOU WANT
TO TALK ABOUT?

23:05.750 --> 23:08.500
FAKES --

23:08.500 --> 23:10.834
PEOPLE WHO
PASS THEMSELVES OFF

23:10.834 --> 23:12.333
AS SOMETHING THEY'RE NOT.

23:12.333 --> 23:13.959
LIKE A PRE-OWNED-CAR
SALESMAN?

23:13.959 --> 23:15.667
A BRAVE POLITICIAN.

23:15.667 --> 23:17.667
A JEW FOR JESUS.

23:17.667 --> 23:20.333
A WOLF
IN SHEEP'S CLOTHING.

23:20.333 --> 23:23.375
IS THAT HOW YOU FEEL, SEAN?

23:23.375 --> 23:25.959
LIKE YOU'RE HIDING
A DARK SECRET?

23:25.959 --> 23:28.667
NO, I WASN'T TALKING
ABOUT ME.

23:28.667 --> 23:29.834
WHO WERE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

23:37.792 --> 23:39.500
YOU.

23:39.500 --> 23:43.375
THAT'S A COMMON FIRST-TIME
REACTION TO THERAPY.

23:43.375 --> 23:45.625
YOU THINK I CAN'T CARE
ABOUT YOU,

23:45.625 --> 23:48.750
THAT I'M ONLY PRETENDING TO CARE
BECAUSE I HAVE ANOTHER MOTIVE.

23:48.750 --> 23:49.750
BINGO.

23:49.750 --> 23:51.458
YOU GOT ME.

23:51.458 --> 23:54.500
I DO HAVE ANOTHER MOTIVE.
IT'S CALLED A PAYCHECK.

23:54.500 --> 23:56.166
BUT THAT DOESN'T MEAN

23:56.166 --> 23:58.375
THAT I CAN'T CARE FOR MY
PATIENTS OR ENJOY MY JOB.

23:58.375 --> 24:00.625
HOW ARE THINGS AT YOUR JOB?

24:00.625 --> 24:03.667
[ SIGHS ] FRUSTRATING,
TO TELL YOU THE TRUTH.

24:03.667 --> 24:06.875
WHAT KIND OF FORENSICS
DO YOU DO?
BLOOD SPATTER.

24:06.875 --> 24:08.709
MOST PEOPLE
CAN'T STAND BLOOD.

24:08.709 --> 24:11.250
I HATE IT.

24:11.250 --> 24:13.875
CATEGORIZING AND ANALYZING
MUST BE VERY SOOTHING FOR YOU.

24:16.792 --> 24:19.500
YEAH, IT IS, ACTUALLY.

24:19.500 --> 24:22.583
SO, OKAY, HOW ARE THINGS
WITH YOUR GIRLFRIEND?

24:22.583 --> 24:24.917
SHE CANCELED LUNCH WITH ME
TO BE WITH HER EX-HUSBAND.

24:24.917 --> 24:26.375
OUCH.

24:26.375 --> 24:28.583
SOUNDS LIKE THINGS ARE OUT
OF YOUR CONTROL RIGHT NOW.

24:28.583 --> 24:31.083
NO WONDER YOU CUT YOURSELF
OFF FROM YOUR EMOTIONS.

24:31.083 --> 24:33.417
THAT WAY YOU NEVER HAVE
TO FEEL POWERLESS.

24:33.417 --> 24:35.583
SO, THEN,
WHAT SHOULD I DO?

24:35.583 --> 24:39.583
ACCEPT THAT CERTAIN THINGS
ARE OUT OF YOUR HANDS. LET GO.

24:42.750 --> 24:45.333
HEY, MORGAN -- I CAN'T BELIEVE,
OUT OF TWO MILLION SPERM,

24:45.333 --> 24:46.583
YOU WERE THE FASTEST SWIMMER.

24:47.583 --> 24:50.250
WHAT ARE YOU
GONNA DO ABOUT IT?

24:50.250 --> 24:52.083
I WANTED TO KILL HIM, DAD.

24:52.083 --> 24:55.792
IT MUST HAVE BEEN TOUGH
FOR YOU TO WALK AWAY, SON.

24:55.792 --> 24:57.792
I'M PROUD THAT YOU DID THAT.

24:57.792 --> 25:01.041
DON'T BE, BECAUSE I STILL
WANT TO KILL HIM.

25:01.041 --> 25:03.125
WHEN'S THAT GONNA GO AWAY?

25:05.583 --> 25:08.333
I THINK I HAVE EVERYTHING
I NEED, MR. PERRY.

25:08.333 --> 25:10.125
WHEN'S THE STORY GONNA RUN?

25:10.125 --> 25:13.125
WELL, THEY'RE SAVING SPACE
FOR TOMORROW, FRONT PAGE.

25:13.125 --> 25:15.333
I JUST GOT TO GET BACK
AND WRITE.

25:15.333 --> 25:18.458
THANKS SO MUCH
FOR YOUR TIME.

25:20.291 --> 25:21.667
LaGuerta:
HOW WAS YOUR INTERVIEW?

25:21.667 --> 25:22.792
IT WAS FINE.

25:22.792 --> 25:24.625
YOU READY TO TALK
ABOUT THE CASE?

25:24.625 --> 25:28.583
SURE, AS SOON AS I GET
TO TALK TO A REPORTER.

25:28.583 --> 25:30.041
YOU JUST DID.

25:30.041 --> 25:31.625
OH, GIVE ME A BREAK.

25:31.625 --> 25:34.375
THAT POSER WAS ONE OF YOUR COP
BUDDIES, BUT NICE TRY.

25:34.375 --> 25:37.667
IN CASE YOU FORGOT, NEIL,
YOU'RE THE ONE IN JAIL.

25:37.667 --> 25:39.333
I CALL THE SHOTS.

25:39.333 --> 25:41.667
I COULD INVOKE MY MIRANDA RIGHTS
AT ANY TIME AND LAWYER UP.

25:41.667 --> 25:44.500
IF YOU WANTED A LAWYER,
YOU'D HAVE ONE BY NOW.

25:47.500 --> 25:49.792
I KNOW YOUR GAME,
LIEUTENANT.

25:49.792 --> 25:53.417
YOU THINK I'M A FRAUD
AND YOU'RE TRYING TO PROVE IT,

25:53.417 --> 25:57.000
BUT THE TRUTH IS
YOU'RE  THE FRAUD.

25:58.875 --> 26:00.500
YOU KNOW WHAT, NEIL?

26:00.500 --> 26:02.625
I'M REALLY NOT IN THE MOOD
FOR YOUR SHIT TODAY.

26:02.625 --> 26:04.250
I FOUND OUT
HOW YOU GOT PROMOTED.

26:11.542 --> 26:13.250
BACK WHEN YOU
AND SERGEANT DOAKES

26:13.250 --> 26:14.709
WERE STILL PARTNERS,

26:14.709 --> 26:16.291
DOAKES GOT THE DROP
ON A MAJOR COKE DEALER,

26:16.291 --> 26:17.875
BROUGHT YOU ALONG
FOR THE RIDE.

26:17.875 --> 26:19.500
HOW DID YOU GET --

26:19.500 --> 26:21.333
WHEN THE PERP BAILED
FROM A THIRD-STORY APARTMENT,

26:21.333 --> 26:23.041
DOAKES TOOK THE FIRE ESCAPE,

26:23.041 --> 26:25.750
SENT YOU TO COVER THE STAIRS
JUST IN CASE.

26:25.750 --> 26:29.542
ONLY YOU GOT LUCKY

26:29.542 --> 26:31.208
AND YOU MADE
THE HEADLINE GRAB,

26:31.208 --> 26:34.041
AND SO THE LEGEND BEGAN.

26:34.041 --> 26:37.291
I WONDER IF DOAKES WOULD HAVE
MADE A GOOD LIEUTENANT.

26:37.291 --> 26:40.542
I DESERVED THAT PROMOTION.

26:40.542 --> 26:43.166
I'M SURE YOU DID.
IT WAS A BIG BUST.

26:43.166 --> 26:46.041
NOT AS BIG AS CATCHING ME,
OF COURSE,

26:46.041 --> 26:48.542
BUT, UH, LET'S BE HONEST.

26:48.542 --> 26:52.709
YOU DIDN'T CATCH ME.
YOUR CAPTAIN DID.

26:58.250 --> 27:00.917
AT LEAST THAT'S WHAT
THEY'RE SAYING ON THE NEWS.

27:08.667 --> 27:10.583
MY THERAPIST WANTS ME TO ACCEPT

27:10.583 --> 27:13.083
THE THINGS
THAT ARE OUT OF MY HANDS.

27:13.083 --> 27:16.041
TRAGICALLY FOR HIM,
HE'S NOT OUT OF MY HANDS,

27:16.041 --> 27:17.917
NOT IF I CAN FIND PROOF

27:17.917 --> 27:20.542
THAT THE DEATH OF AT LEAST
THREE WOMEN UNDER HIS CARE

27:20.542 --> 27:22.333
WAS NOT A COINCIDENCE.

27:22.333 --> 27:23.750
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

27:28.875 --> 27:30.333
BREAKING AND ENTERING.

27:43.166 --> 27:45.333
I HOPE HE GOT MY GOOD SIDE.

27:52.834 --> 27:56.792
NOW, WHAT'S HE RECORDING
FOR POSTERITY'S SAKE?

28:09.417 --> 28:12.625
GOODBYE, DEXTER.

28:14.125 --> 28:16.583
HELLO, LADIES.

28:16.583 --> 28:20.166
I NEED
ANOTHER PRESCRIPTION.

28:20.166 --> 28:24.291
Dr. Meridian: I'M SORRY,
VANESSA. I CAN'T DO THAT.

28:24.291 --> 28:28.291
JUST ONE MORE, PLEASE.

28:28.291 --> 28:31.834
WE TALKED ABOUT THIS.

28:31.834 --> 28:34.917
THE ANTIDEPRESSANTS
WERE A TEMPORARY CRUTCH

28:34.917 --> 28:38.166
SO THAT YOU COULD START
TAKING STEPS ON YOUR OWN.

28:38.166 --> 28:41.792
BUT YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND.
I CAN'T DO THIS ON MY OWN.

28:41.792 --> 28:44.333
I CAN'T EVEN
GET OUT OF FUCKING BED.

28:47.875 --> 28:51.792
I JUST -- I WANT TO DIE.

28:51.792 --> 28:54.667
LOOK AT ME.

28:54.667 --> 28:57.709
I UNDERSTAND THE APPEAL
OF DEATH, OKAY?

28:57.709 --> 29:00.500
NO MORE PAIN.

29:00.500 --> 29:03.834
ALL THE CAREER PRESSURE,
THE HOPELESSNESS, GONE.

29:05.291 --> 29:06.875
IN MANY CULTURES,

29:06.875 --> 29:08.709
THERE'S NO STIGMA ATTACHED
TO TAKING ONE'S LIFE.

29:08.709 --> 29:11.542
SUICIDE'S RESPECTED,
EVEN REVERED

29:11.542 --> 29:14.458
AS A MATTER
OF PERSONAL CONSCIENCE.

29:14.458 --> 29:16.875
HOW DO MOST PEOPLE DO IT?

29:16.875 --> 29:20.542
WELL, PAINKILLERS
ARE THE MOST COMMON.

29:20.542 --> 29:22.667
BUT THEY'RE
ENTIRELY UNRELIABLE.

29:22.667 --> 29:26.333
THE TRULY COURAGEOUS
OF HEART...

29:26.333 --> 29:27.875
USE GUNS.

29:30.208 --> 29:32.375
YOU TOOK WOMEN
WHO TRUSTED YOU

29:32.375 --> 29:35.000
AT THEIR WEAKEST
POSSIBLE MOMENT,

29:35.000 --> 29:38.542
AND RATHER THAN HELP THEM,
YOU SUGGESTED THEY END IT ALL.

29:38.542 --> 29:43.000
GOD, YOU EVEN GAVE THEM
PERMISSION TO USE A GUN.

29:43.000 --> 29:45.041
OH, YOU'RE A MEAN ONE,
MR. SHRINK.

29:45.041 --> 29:48.041
CREATE THEIR DRUG ADDICTION,
PULL THEM OFF,

29:48.041 --> 29:51.959
THEN FILL THEIR ADDLED HEADS
WITH NOBLE THOUGHTS OF SUICIDE.

29:51.959 --> 29:54.625
I THINK I'VE HAD
A BREAKTHROUGH IN THERAPY.

29:54.625 --> 29:56.417
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

30:05.792 --> 30:08.917
HEY, I GOT YOUR TEXTS.
IS EVERYTHING...

30:12.917 --> 30:14.750
...OKAY?

30:14.750 --> 30:18.333
IT IS NOW.

30:18.333 --> 30:20.917
OKAY, JUST,
I WANTED TO SEE YOU.

30:20.917 --> 30:24.000
I FELT BAD
ABOUT MISSING LUNCH

30:24.000 --> 30:25.834
TO BE WITH PAUL
AND THE KIDS.

30:25.834 --> 30:28.125
I HOPE YOU DIDN'T GET
THE WRONG IDEA.

30:28.125 --> 30:30.917
NO, OF COURSE NOT.

30:34.458 --> 30:36.000
HOW'D IT GO?

30:36.000 --> 30:40.291
REALLY GOOD
AND INCREDIBLY SCARY.

30:40.291 --> 30:42.667
FOR THE FIRST TIME
IN A LONG WHILE,

30:42.667 --> 30:44.208
I SAW HOW EASY IT WOULD BE

30:44.208 --> 30:46.500
FOR ME TO FALL BACK
INTO MY OLD LIFE.

30:46.500 --> 30:48.291
WHY IS THAT SCARY?

30:48.291 --> 30:52.959
BECAUSE...
I LIKE MY NEW LIFE.

30:52.959 --> 30:54.709
AND I FINALLY FEEL LIKE
I'M IN CONTROL.

30:54.709 --> 30:56.458
I NEVER FELT
THAT WAY WITH PAUL.

30:56.458 --> 30:59.291
I DO WITH YOU.

31:06.709 --> 31:08.583
THIS IS A DISASTER.

31:08.583 --> 31:10.959
I CHOSE RITA
BECAUSE SHE WAS DAMAGED.

31:10.959 --> 31:13.542
IF SHE GETS BETTER,
I'LL LOSE HER FOR SURE.

31:17.542 --> 31:19.709
I'M READY, DEXTER.

31:27.458 --> 31:29.709
OH.

31:29.709 --> 31:32.834
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT I'VE BEEN SO AFRAID OF.

31:32.834 --> 31:35.583
YOU'RE
THE PERFECT BOYFRIEND.

31:41.875 --> 31:44.250
I WANT YOU TO SPEND
THE NIGHT, FOR REAL.

31:52.834 --> 31:54.458
I'M SO SORRY.

31:54.458 --> 31:58.792
I CAME OVER HERE BECAUSE
I THOUGHT SOMETHING WAS WRONG.

31:58.792 --> 32:01.542
BUT TONIGHT'S REALLY NOT
A GOOD NIGHT.

32:01.542 --> 32:03.917
I'M RIGHT
IN THE MIDDLE OF A CASE.

32:03.917 --> 32:07.375
I'M WAY TOO DISTRACTED.

32:07.375 --> 32:09.667
NOW? IT'S SO LATE.

32:09.667 --> 32:13.041
THAT'S ALL THE MORE REASON
TO GET BACK TO WORK.

32:13.041 --> 32:15.875
THE CLOCK'S TICKING.

32:15.875 --> 32:17.125
HERE.

32:19.583 --> 32:23.875
BUT I'LL CALL YOU
TOMORROW. OKAY?

32:23.875 --> 32:25.709
OKAY? OKAY?

32:25.709 --> 32:27.208
OKAY.

32:30.667 --> 32:32.709
SHIT.

32:32.709 --> 32:34.875
I CAN'T HAVE SEX WITH RITA.

32:34.875 --> 32:36.667
EVERY TIME
I SLEEP WITH A WOMAN,

32:36.667 --> 32:38.917
SHE SEES ME FOR WHAT
I REALLY AM -- EMPTY --

32:38.917 --> 32:41.166
AND THEN SHE'S GONE.

32:46.208 --> 32:49.000
BUT I DON'T WANT RITA TO GO,

32:49.000 --> 32:51.792
WHICH MEANS I HAVE
TO DEAL WITH THIS.

32:51.792 --> 32:53.625
I CAN'T KILL MERIDIAN YET.

32:53.625 --> 32:56.208
I NEED ANOTHER THERAPY SESSION.

32:56.208 --> 32:59.583
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

33:10.709 --> 33:13.417
STAY WHERE YOU ARE.
I'M ARMED.

33:13.417 --> 33:14.917
[ GIGGLES ]

33:14.917 --> 33:16.875
WITH BAD PUNS?

33:16.875 --> 33:19.583
MMM.

33:22.500 --> 33:24.667
YOU SAID YOU NEEDED
A FAVOR. WHAT'S UP?

33:24.667 --> 33:26.291
TAKE OFF YOUR PANTS.

33:26.291 --> 33:28.083
OH, I SHOULD HAVE KNOWN
IT WAS THAT KIND OF FAVOR.

33:28.083 --> 33:29.792
YOU NEVER ASK ME TO COME BY
BEFORE WORK.

33:29.792 --> 33:32.291
NO, BUT I LIKE
THE WAY YOU THINK.

33:32.291 --> 33:36.250
I HAVE A PATIENT WHO LOST
BOTH HER LEGS IN A CAR ACCIDENT,

33:36.250 --> 33:37.458
REALLY BRUTAL.

33:37.458 --> 33:40.291
LIKE YOUR MOM?

33:40.291 --> 33:43.291
WHICH IS WHY I WANT TO DO
SOMETHING SPECIAL FOR HER.

33:43.291 --> 33:45.500
I WANT TO GIVE HER

33:45.500 --> 33:48.542
A NEW SMOKIN' PAIR
OF LEGS --

33:48.542 --> 33:50.000
YOURS.
NO.

33:50.000 --> 33:52.208
LET ME JUST TAKE A CAST.
NO WAY. NO.

33:52.208 --> 33:53.500
IT'LL TAKE
20 MINUTES, TOPS.

33:53.500 --> 33:55.375
COME ON, PLEASE?

33:55.375 --> 33:58.709
STOP BEING SUCH A CHICK.

33:58.709 --> 34:00.834
SIT DOWN.

34:07.000 --> 34:10.166
[ GIGGLES ]

34:20.625 --> 34:22.166
FEELS GOOD.

34:35.625 --> 34:37.417
CAN I MAKE
ONE OF YOUR COCK?

34:37.417 --> 34:39.750
THAT'D BE A HELL OF A STORY
TO TELL THE BULLPEN, HUH?

34:39.750 --> 34:42.792
NOT LIKELY.

34:42.792 --> 34:44.792
I HAVEN'T TOLD ANYONE
ABOUT US.

34:44.792 --> 34:47.709
EMBARRASSED ABOUT BANGING
CAPTAIN HOOK?

34:47.709 --> 34:50.250
NOT EVEN A LITTLE.

34:50.250 --> 34:51.542
THEN WHY?

34:53.875 --> 34:56.959
I GUESS THIS MATTERS TO ME.

34:56.959 --> 35:00.709
SO IF I TALK ABOUT IT
AND IT GOES AWAY,

35:00.709 --> 35:03.417
I'M ACTUALLY LOSING
SOMETHING.

35:05.542 --> 35:08.208
THAT RETARDED?

35:10.875 --> 35:13.250
NO.

35:13.250 --> 35:15.375
I GOT TO TELL YOU,

35:15.375 --> 35:18.000
I'M NOT GOING ANYWHERE.

35:18.000 --> 35:20.792
SERIOUSLY?

35:27.625 --> 35:31.500
AND NEITHER ARE YOU,

35:31.500 --> 35:33.834
'CAUSE I GOT YOUR LEG.

35:45.417 --> 35:46.917
WHERE THE HELL
YOU BEEN?

35:46.917 --> 35:48.542
WITH MY BOYFRIEND.

35:48.542 --> 35:50.291
BOYFRIEND?

35:50.291 --> 35:53.625
YEP. WE JUST FUCKED
IN HIS OFFICE.

35:53.625 --> 35:56.834
AND WE'RE HAVING DINNER
TOMORROW NIGHT.

35:56.834 --> 35:58.583
YOU LOOKING FOR ME?

35:58.583 --> 36:00.750
YEAH. SHUT THE DOOR.

36:04.208 --> 36:06.875
DID YOU TELL ANYONE
ABOUT OUR BUST,

36:06.875 --> 36:08.834
THE ONE
THAT GOT ME PROMOTED?

36:08.834 --> 36:10.208
NO.

36:10.208 --> 36:13.375
NOBODY IN THE PRESS?

36:13.375 --> 36:15.500
MARIA, WE TALKED ABOUT THIS
WHEN IT HAPPENED.

36:15.500 --> 36:18.291
IT WOULD FUCK UP YOUR REP AND
MAKE ME LOOK LIKE A WHINY BITCH.

36:18.291 --> 36:20.041
IT'S BAD FOR BOTH OF US.

36:20.041 --> 36:22.792
SO THEN THE ONLY WAY
TO ACCESS THAT INFORMATION

36:22.792 --> 36:25.166
WOULD BE TO READ
TO POLICE REPORT, RIGHT?

36:25.166 --> 36:27.375
I GUESS.

36:29.542 --> 36:31.792
WE HAVE TO HAVE
OUR FIREWALL CHECKED.

36:34.083 --> 36:37.291
SHE WAS SITTING ON TOP OF ME,
BASICALLY NAKED...

36:39.792 --> 36:42.792
...ASKING ME
TO SPEND THE NIGHT,

36:42.792 --> 36:44.667
AND I DIDN'T KNOW
WHAT TO DO.

36:44.667 --> 36:47.291
IT'S OKAY, SEAN.
DON'T BEAT YOURSELF UP.

36:47.291 --> 36:50.083
YOUR GIRLFRIEND REALLY MEANS
SOMETHING TO YOU.

36:50.083 --> 36:51.500
I KNOW THAT.

36:51.500 --> 36:53.875
IF SHE MEANS SOMETHING,
WHY DO I RUN AWAY FROM HER?

36:53.875 --> 36:56.291
THE SAME REASON YOU WORK SO HARD
TO SHUT EVERYBODY ELSE OUT.

36:56.291 --> 36:58.000
YOU'RE AFRAID
THEY WON'T LIKE WHAT THEY SEE.

36:58.000 --> 37:01.834
YEAH,
I THINK YOU'RE RIGHT.

37:01.834 --> 37:03.333
HOW CAN I CHANGE THAT?

37:03.333 --> 37:05.375
WELL, FOR STARTERS,
YOU ACCEPT THE FACT

37:05.375 --> 37:08.792
THAT WE ALL HAVE A BIG, BAD WOLF
HIDING INSIDE OF US,

37:08.792 --> 37:11.709
A DARKNESS WE DON'T WANT
ANYONE ELSE TO SEE.

37:11.709 --> 37:13.125
DO YOU?

37:13.125 --> 37:14.667
OF COURSE I DO.

37:16.834 --> 37:18.000
REALLY?

37:18.000 --> 37:19.417
MM-HMM.

37:19.417 --> 37:21.709
AND HOW DO YOU DEAL
WITH YOUR WOLF?

37:21.709 --> 37:25.583
WELL, FIRST OF ALL, I ACCEPTED
THAT IT WAS THERE.

37:25.583 --> 37:27.417
I MADE FRIENDS WITH IT.

37:29.083 --> 37:33.458
AND NOW I JUST LET IT OUT
FOR A BIG MEAL ONCE IN A WHILE.

37:33.458 --> 37:36.583
AT LEAST THREE TIMES
THAT WE KNOW ABOUT.

37:38.417 --> 37:40.709
CAN WE GET BACK
TO THE SEX THING?

37:40.709 --> 37:42.208
THIS IS ALL ABOUT SEX.

37:42.208 --> 37:45.083
THE REASON YOU AVOID
SEXUAL INTIMACY

37:45.083 --> 37:47.041
IS BECAUSE YOU DON'T WANT
TO SURRENDER CONTROL.

37:47.041 --> 37:48.625
NO, I'VE
SURRENDERED CONTROL.

37:48.625 --> 37:50.709
IT'S NOT LIKE MY GIRLFRIEND
HASN'T BEEN,

37:50.709 --> 37:52.250
YOU KNOW,
SOUTH OF THE BORDER.

37:52.250 --> 37:54.083
THAT'S NOT
WHAT I'M TALKING ABOUT.

37:54.083 --> 37:56.041
INTIMACY --

37:56.041 --> 37:59.375
REALLY LETTING GO
FACE-TO-FACE --

37:59.375 --> 38:01.750
THERE'S NOTHING
MORE DIFFICULT THAN THAT.

38:01.750 --> 38:04.208
THE MINUTE YOU START
TO ACCEPT WHO YOU ARE,

38:04.208 --> 38:06.375
YOU JUST MIGHT
FEEL FREE ENOUGH

38:06.375 --> 38:08.375
TO SHARE
THAT INTIMACY TOGETHER.

38:17.375 --> 38:19.041
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

38:19.041 --> 38:20.917
I'D LIKE TO TALK YOU THROUGH
A DEEP-RELAXATION TECHNIQUE.

38:20.917 --> 38:23.291
IT MIGHT BRING
SOME THINGS TO THE SURFACE.

38:23.291 --> 38:24.917
WHAT KINDS OF THINGS?

38:24.917 --> 38:27.417
WELL, THERE MUST HAVE BEEN
A TIME IN YOUR LIFE

38:27.417 --> 38:29.333
WHEN YOU FELT
POWERLESS, RIGHT?

38:29.333 --> 38:33.500
FOSTER CHILD, NO CONTROL
OVER YOUR DESTINY.

38:33.500 --> 38:35.875
IF WE CAN BRING SOME OF THOSE
MEMORIES TO THE SURFACE,

38:35.875 --> 38:37.875
WE MIGHT FIND THE ROOT
OF YOUR CONTROL ISSUES.

38:37.875 --> 38:40.375
FIRST, I WANT YOU
TO CLOSE YOUR EYES

38:40.375 --> 38:42.417
AND FOCUS ON YOUR BREATHING.

38:42.417 --> 38:44.750
I WANT YOU TO COUNT
EACH BREATH, OKAY?

38:44.750 --> 38:48.875
IN, 1, AND OUT, 2.

38:48.875 --> 38:51.041
JUST GIVE IT A TRY.

38:51.041 --> 38:52.750
THIS IS RIDICULOUS.

38:52.750 --> 38:54.583
I COULD BE KILLING HIM
RIGHT NOW.

38:54.583 --> 38:58.792
NOW I WANT YOU TO THINK
OF A TIME

38:58.792 --> 39:04.291
WHEN YOU FELT COMPLETELY
AND TOTALLY POWERLESS.

39:11.500 --> 39:13.959
HEY, MORGAN.
YOU STILL FUCKING YOUR SISTER?

39:13.959 --> 39:15.291
LEAVE ME ALONE, JOSH.

39:23.333 --> 39:25.542
I TOLD YOU TO WALK AWAY.

39:26.792 --> 39:28.667
GOD DAMN IT, DEXTER.

39:28.667 --> 39:32.333
THERE ARE CONSEQUENCES
TO EVERYTHING YOU DO IN LIFE.

39:32.333 --> 39:35.959
LOSE CONTROL, BECOME POWERLESS,
AND IT'S OVER.

39:35.959 --> 39:37.333
I FOUND THE GRAVE, SON.

39:37.333 --> 39:38.709
YOU'RE SAYING
I'LL BE LIKE THIS FOREVER.

39:40.208 --> 39:42.125
[ CHILD SCREAMING ]

39:42.125 --> 39:47.041
MOMMY!

39:47.041 --> 39:48.750
I HAVE TO GET OUT OF HERE.

39:48.750 --> 39:50.166
HEY, HEY, HEY, HEY.
WHOA. WHOA. WHOA.

39:50.166 --> 39:51.458
SEAN, COME HERE.

39:51.458 --> 39:53.458
SEAN, SEAN.

39:53.458 --> 39:55.500
SEAN!

39:55.500 --> 39:57.583
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

40:10.834 --> 40:13.083
OH, MY GOD.

40:16.709 --> 40:18.583
ARE YOU OKAY?

40:40.917 --> 40:43.041
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

41:04.041 --> 41:06.291
STAY. STAY WITH ME.

42:06.291 --> 42:07.959
[ SIGHS ]

42:11.208 --> 42:13.125
YOU'RE SWEET.

42:16.291 --> 42:17.959
I AM?

42:17.959 --> 42:21.458
NEXT TIME, WE'LL FIGURE OUT
WHAT TO TELL THE KIDS

42:21.458 --> 42:24.625
SO YOU DON'T HAVE
TO SNEAK OUT LIKE THIS.

42:26.875 --> 42:29.667
YOU WANT THERE TO BE
A NEXT TIME?

42:29.667 --> 42:33.834
AND A TIME AFTER THAT.

42:33.834 --> 42:36.000
DON'T YOU?

42:41.208 --> 42:44.959
NO. I MEAN, YEAH.

42:44.959 --> 42:47.000
I JUST...

42:50.542 --> 42:54.333
I DIDN'T FREAK YOU OUT?

42:54.333 --> 42:56.125
WHY WOULD YOU THINK THAT?

42:56.125 --> 42:59.125
DEXTER, THERE'S NOTHING
YOU COULD EVER DO

42:59.125 --> 43:00.750
THAT WOULD SCARE ME AWAY.

43:15.041 --> 43:17.125
I REALLY HOPE
YOU CAME TO APOLOGIZE.

43:17.125 --> 43:19.375
NOPE.
I CAME FOR A CONSULT.

43:19.375 --> 43:21.625
AND YOU BROUGHT BEVERAGES?

43:21.625 --> 43:23.875
I GOT THIS ON LOAN
FROM THE MORGUE.

43:23.875 --> 43:26.917
NOW, I COULD USE
AN EXPERT OPINION,

43:26.917 --> 43:29.333
SPECIFICALLY
YOUR EXPERT OPINION.

43:29.333 --> 43:32.625
SEE, WE CAN'T FIGURE OUT

43:32.625 --> 43:35.583
EXACTLY HOW THE KILLER
CUT OFF THIS HEAD.

43:35.583 --> 43:37.667
CAN YOU?

43:37.667 --> 43:39.375
NOPE.

43:39.375 --> 43:42.583
REALLY?
I THINK YOU CAN.

43:42.583 --> 43:44.667
I MEAN, YOU CHOP PEOPLE UP,
DON'T YOU?

43:44.667 --> 43:46.375
MAYBE YOU NEED
A CLOSER LOOK.

43:46.375 --> 43:48.709
NO. KEEP IT AWAY.

43:48.709 --> 43:50.959
[ SOBBING ]

43:54.625 --> 43:56.750
I TALKED
TO THE MEDICAL EXAMINER.

43:56.750 --> 43:58.667
HE COULDN'T CONFIRM
HOW YOUR MOM DIED.

43:58.667 --> 44:00.709
SAID IT MIGHT HAVE BEEN
A HEART ATTACK.

44:00.709 --> 44:01.917
I KILLED HER.

44:01.917 --> 44:03.750
YOU DON'T HAVE THE BALLS.

44:03.750 --> 44:06.083
I MEAN, YOU HAD TO WAIT
TILL SHE DIED TO CHOP HER UP.

44:06.083 --> 44:10.125
AND EVEN THEN YOU WERE TOO
SQUEAMISH TO CUT OFF HER HEAD.

44:10.125 --> 44:13.709
NOT EXACTLY THE SAME
AS STUFFING ROADKILL, IS IT?

44:13.709 --> 44:15.417
OH, FUCK YOU.

44:15.417 --> 44:18.542
SERIAL KILLERS GET ALL
THE GLORY, DON'T THEY, NEIL?

44:18.542 --> 44:20.709
ESPECIALLY
THE ICE-TRUCK KILLER.

44:20.709 --> 44:22.834
YOU KNOW, YOU'RE NOT
THE FIRST GROUPIE

44:22.834 --> 44:25.333
TO TAKE CREDIT
FOR SOMEONE ELSE'S WORK.

44:25.333 --> 44:26.583
OH, BULLSHIT.

44:26.583 --> 44:28.375
I KNOW DETAILS ABOUT THE CASE,

44:28.375 --> 44:30.125
THINGS THAT WEREN'T
PUBLISHED IN THE NEWSPAPERS.

44:30.125 --> 44:32.583
THAT'S BECAUSE YOU HACKED
INTO OUR COMPUTER SYSTEM.

44:32.583 --> 44:34.625
I HAD THE I.T. GUYS
CHECK OUR FIREWALL.

44:34.625 --> 44:37.417
THE DMZ WAS BREACHED.
YOU READ ALL OUR POLICE REPORTS.

44:37.417 --> 44:40.291
YOU EVEN GOT YOURSELF
A NICE PANELED CAR LAST MONTH.

44:40.291 --> 44:41.417
NICE TOUCH, BY THE WAY.

44:41.417 --> 44:42.959
WHY ARE YOU DOING THIS?

44:42.959 --> 44:45.792
BECAUSE YOU'RE NOT A KILLER.

44:45.792 --> 44:50.125
YOU'RE A COWARD AND A FAKE,
AREN'T YOU?

44:54.375 --> 44:57.458
MAYBE YOU NEED
ANOTHER LOOK.

44:57.458 --> 44:59.792
NO, TAKE IT AWAY.

45:02.291 --> 45:05.625
ALL RIGHT, I LIED, OKAY?

45:07.667 --> 45:09.959
JUST, I NEED YOU

45:09.959 --> 45:12.709
TO TAKE IT AWAY FROM ME...

45:12.709 --> 45:14.667
PLEASE.

45:24.750 --> 45:26.917
SO, WHAT'S ON YOUR MIND,
LIEUTENANT?

45:26.917 --> 45:29.583
WE GOT A LOT TO GET DONE
BEFORE PERRY'S TRIAL.

45:29.583 --> 45:33.125
YEAH, ABOUT THAT TRIAL --
I'VE GOT SOME BAD NEWS.

45:33.125 --> 45:36.417
PERRY RECANTED HIS CONFESSION
THIS MORNING.

45:36.417 --> 45:38.375
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

45:38.375 --> 45:40.834
I WAS GOING OVER SOME DETAILS
WITH HIM AT COUNTY,

45:40.834 --> 45:43.542
AND HE ADMITTED THAT
HE GAVE US A FALSE CONFESSION.

45:45.166 --> 45:46.458
HE'S A WANNABE, TOM.

45:46.458 --> 45:49.166
JUST WANTED HIS 15 MINUTES,
THAT'S ALL.

45:49.166 --> 45:50.917
HOW DO YOU KNOW WHICH TIME
HE WAS LYING?

45:52.709 --> 45:55.166
ALL DUE RESPECT, MARIA,
IF WE DROPPED CHARGES

45:55.166 --> 45:57.542
EVERY TIME SOMEONE
RECANTED HIS CONFESSION,

45:57.542 --> 45:59.750
OUR JAILS WOULD BE EMPTY.

45:59.750 --> 46:01.500
WE'RE GOING TO TRIAL.

46:01.500 --> 46:04.875
ALL DUE RESPECT, CAPTAIN,
THAT'S REALLY NOT UP TO YOU.

46:06.333 --> 46:08.959
IT'S UP TO THE D.A.

46:08.959 --> 46:11.333
Man: I UNDERSTAND
YOUR FRUSTRATION, MARIA,

46:11.333 --> 46:13.208
BUT I REVIEWED
THE D.A. WORK SHEETS.

46:13.208 --> 46:14.959
THE EVIDENCE IS COMPELLING.

46:14.959 --> 46:16.583
WE'LL MOVE FORWARD
WITH THE TRIAL AS PLANNED.

46:22.166 --> 46:24.583
FAIR ENOUGH.

46:24.583 --> 46:28.041
IF THAT'S WHAT YOU TWO WANT,
I'M FULLY BEHIND IT.

46:28.041 --> 46:30.667
I WAS REALLY WORRIED ABOUT YOU.
YOU SURE YOU'RE ALL RIGHT?

46:30.667 --> 46:32.333
I KEPT CALLING YOUR HOUSE,

46:32.333 --> 46:34.083
BUT I THINK THE NUMBER
YOU GAVE ME DIDN'T WORK.

46:34.083 --> 46:35.750
YOU WOULDN'T HAVE
REACHED ME ANYWAY,

46:35.750 --> 46:37.250
'CAUSE I WAS
AT MY GIRLFRIEND'S.

46:38.917 --> 46:43.542
I SPENT THE NIGHT,
FACE-TO-FACE.

46:43.542 --> 46:47.542
SEAN, THAT'S VERY GOOD.

46:47.542 --> 46:50.333
IT'S ALL GOOD, DOCTOR.

46:50.333 --> 46:52.417
I EVEN STOPPED WORRYING
ABOUT THAT FRIEND OF MINE

46:52.417 --> 46:54.000
WHO'S BEEN OUT OF TOUCH.

46:54.000 --> 46:55.959
YOU CAN'T CONTROL
OTHER PEOPLE, YOU KNOW?

46:55.959 --> 46:58.000
THIS IS A REAL BREAKTHROUGH.
YOU SHOULD BE PROUD OF YOURSELF.

46:58.000 --> 46:59.917
I AM PROUD.

47:03.333 --> 47:05.750
[ CHUCKLES ]

47:05.750 --> 47:07.250
TRUTH BE TOLD,

47:07.250 --> 47:10.417
I NEVER EXPECTED
TO MAKE PROGRESS IN THERAPY.

47:10.417 --> 47:11.834
THAT'S NOT TRUE.

47:11.834 --> 47:13.500
IF THAT WERE TRUE,

47:13.500 --> 47:16.917
YOU NEVER WOULD HAVE COME
IN HERE IN THE FIRST PLACE.

47:18.792 --> 47:20.583
WHAT DO YOU WANT
TO FOCUS ON TODAY?

47:20.583 --> 47:22.458
I'M GLAD YOU ASKED THAT.

47:27.542 --> 47:30.750
I'M GONNA TELL YOU
SOMETHING

47:30.750 --> 47:33.041
THAT I'VE NEVER TOLD
ANYONE BEFORE.

47:33.041 --> 47:34.667
OKAY.

47:36.500 --> 47:38.792
I'M A SERIAL KILLER.

47:42.458 --> 47:46.000
OH, GOD.

47:46.000 --> 47:51.542
OH, THAT FEELS SO AMAZING
TO SAY OUT LOUD.

47:51.542 --> 47:53.333
WELL, YOU MUST BE LETTING GO,

47:53.333 --> 47:55.291
BECAUSE I'VE NEVER HEARD YOU
MAKE A JOKE BEFORE.

47:55.291 --> 47:57.458
I'M NOT JOKING.
I KILL PEOPLE.

47:57.458 --> 48:01.000
WHEW! THERE IT IS AGAIN.

48:04.333 --> 48:06.875
YOU SHOULD TRY IT.

48:06.875 --> 48:08.417
I KNOW.

48:08.417 --> 48:13.000
YOUR BIG, BAD WOLF HAS RACKED UP
A TIDY LITTLE DEATH TOLL.

48:15.417 --> 48:17.041
I'M JUST KIDDING.

48:17.041 --> 48:19.041
I DISABLED THE CAMERAS,
AND I COPIED THE FILES.

48:19.041 --> 48:21.333
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

48:21.333 --> 48:23.959
THEN FOCUS ON YOUR BREATHING,
AND MAYBE YOU'LL REMEMBER --

48:23.959 --> 48:25.375
MEGHAN, CAROLYN, VANESSA.

48:25.375 --> 48:26.792
THOSE SESSIONS
ARE CONFIDENTIAL.

48:26.792 --> 48:28.625
I'M A CONTROL FREAK,
I KNOW.

48:28.625 --> 48:30.500
BUT I WATCHED
YOUR HOME MOVIES.

48:30.500 --> 48:34.083
IT'S AMAZING STUFF -- DRUGS,
GUNS, AND A CRAZY PSYCHIATRIST.

48:34.083 --> 48:37.000
NO WONDER YOU'RE SO WELL VERSED
IN CONTROL ISSUES.

48:37.000 --> 48:39.041
YOU GOT
QUITE THE GOD COMPLEX.

48:39.041 --> 48:41.375
THIS SESSION'S OVER.

48:41.375 --> 48:43.041
[ CHOKING ]

48:50.959 --> 48:53.125
NOT SO FAST, DOC.

49:12.250 --> 49:13.709
YOU'RE AWAKE.

49:13.709 --> 49:16.875
SHALL WE ANALYZE
YOUR DREAMS?

49:18.875 --> 49:20.959
NO. THAT'S RIGHT.

49:20.959 --> 49:23.625
YOU'VE ALREADY TOLD ME
EVERYTHING I NEED TO KNOW,

49:23.625 --> 49:27.417
EXCEPT WHY POWERFUL WOMEN?

49:27.417 --> 49:31.542
YOU TOOK POWERFUL WOMEN
AND MADE THEM POWERLESS.

49:31.542 --> 49:35.291
THEY LEFT BEHIND
FAMILIES, CHILDREN.

49:44.583 --> 49:47.208
I HAVE TO CONFESS,
I'M A LITTLE CONFLICTED.

49:47.208 --> 49:50.166
YOU'VE HELPED ME MAKE
A MAJOR SELF-DISCOVERY.

49:53.750 --> 49:56.792
THE FACT
THAT I'M A KILLER...

50:09.959 --> 50:13.208
...THAT'S SOMETHING
I CAN'T CONTROL.

50:19.959 --> 50:23.750
YOU HELPED ME TO ACCEPT
WHAT I REALLY AM.

50:23.750 --> 50:25.458
I'M GRATEFUL FOR THAT.

50:25.458 --> 50:29.000
BUT...

50:29.000 --> 50:32.792
I WAS RAISED WITH A CERTAIN SET
OF PRINCIPLES.

50:35.667 --> 50:37.792
